      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.6/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/7926bbfe-1ffe-11e5-9b0e-5254006e85c2).  Ran 11 tests.  No failures in this session, but a previous session failed for this commit.",
